@itinerary_be.WebAPI_HostAddress = http://localhost:5238

### Weather Forecast
GET {{itinerary_be.WebAPI_HostAddress}}/weatherforecast/
Accept: application/json

###

### Create Trip
POST {{itinerary_be.WebAPI_HostAddress}}/api/trips
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Summer Vacation 2026",
  "startDate": "2026-07-15",
  "endDate": "2026-08-15"
}

###

### Get All Trips
GET {{itinerary_be.WebAPI_HostAddress}}/api/trips
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Trip by ID (replace {tripId} with actual ID)
GET {{itinerary_be.WebAPI_HostAddress}}/api/trips/{{tripId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Update Trip (replace {tripId} with actual ID)
PUT {{itinerary_be.WebAPI_HostAddress}}/api/trips/{{tripId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Summer Vacation 2026 - Updated",
  "startDate": "2026-07-20",
  "endDate": "2026-08-20"
}

###

### Delete Trip (replace {tripId} with actual ID)
DELETE {{itinerary_be.WebAPI_HostAddress}}/api/trips/{{tripId}}

###

